{"tid":239472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[粉嶺撚] 屋企樓下附近有隻貓","createTime":"2017-05-11T16:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T18:10:01.000Z","uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d96b0d925cbf70caa85e2b232e650be26fcc665b","tid":239472,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲打住粉嶺嘉福見過呢隻貓？<br />\n平時好少係呢邊見到有流浪貓狗<br />\n岩岩行過果陣時見到有d野係草叢行過於是去望下<br />\n點知係隻貓黎<br />\n佢見到我即刻行過黎痴住我<br />\n似係流浪左無耐(?) 定有人養(?)<br />\n正常流浪貓係咪應該會避忌d？<br />\n<br />\n希望只係有人咁岩走失左隻貓/ 放貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而唔係棄養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/12/004126_dbedf93cc4949ac101c5620459f9ea7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2F004126_dbedf93cc4949ac101c5620459f9ea7d.jpg&h=b177d116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uu36f4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUu36f4y.jpg&h=ee9ed446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62869bS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62869bS.jpg&h=8eafd6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自膠先，之後我俾隻飛曱甴嚇走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後行返過去又搵佢唔到了"},{"pid":"94394dae7afe1dfc12ee51cfe7ca8594eacb39cc","tid":239472,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"好似好可愛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d785abf304645a5baf77a594c5cc02f4b04d4389","tid":239472,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似好可愛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係咁叫<br />\n同埋好似搵緊d野咁<br />\n唔通搵緊主人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31718f3f015bd40294e289c3928eecc60c88f535","tid":239472,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"原來我開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fed3a17a669e7fe1d4635246d9f9c2f638098e","tid":239472,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似好可愛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係咁叫<br />\n同埋好似搵緊d野咁<br />\n唔通搵緊主人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想可以發動技能<br />\nbtw仲係搵唔返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca65dee4c2534cee144163aec976c40b2aa8bcfd","tid":239472,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似好可愛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係咁叫<br />\n同埋好似搵緊d野咁<br />\n唔通搵緊主人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想可以發動技能<br />\nbtw仲係搵唔返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我走左喇<br />\n企企下好驚又有飛曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d033bc609925bf5690cd0af25ae9443730475072","tid":239472,"uid":90113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"一年前左加我屋企樓下都試過有隻咁既色既貓 一見到人就痴過黎 仲跟我返屋企"},{"pid":"429f0439dd731bca523feb36bdc3330ca9164f01","tid":239472,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年前左加我屋企樓下都試過有隻咁既色既貓 一見到人就痴過黎 仲跟我返屋企</blockquote><br />\n巴打都係呢頭附近？<br />\n呢個size係咪已經係成貓<br />\n我無養開貓唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但見佢自己一個係咁叫好似好慘咁"},{"pid":"75511e32a2bff1f1e8289e6811aa6acb15a9140b","tid":239472,"uid":90113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"搵返啲相 我見到果隻係咁既樣 應該唔係同一隻<br />\n我都唔係住粉嶺區<br />\n不過都係一年前既事啦 果排返屋企見到佢真係超幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdTeLp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdTeLp0.jpg&h=872114c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b985f8415813fb87dc254dfd24446df2943a8b90","tid":239472,"uid":38895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"技能發動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9374fb67e670cbcef5fd39d1f66fadbbf7507f6","tid":239472,"uid":109302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"不過希望唔好係走失"},{"pid":"c4f58bece02e9bbd2420227c4bf64213f3911ad5","tid":239472,"uid":84967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過希望唔好係走失</blockquote><br />\n佢係咁喵好似好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經放緊係d fb gp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有人見到"},{"pid":"2d9eb7eb5a258182ec642ab7e088f396574382d2","tid":239472,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T18:10:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以影一張你對腳既相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}